{"tid":298033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲平時跑開步？","createTime":"2017-06-26T03:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T15:52:23.000Z","uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07faf877560244171c3e227c7d98e6bc56628ca8","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"最近開始跑步 但跑得好慢 見好似冇乜跑步group 所以開一個交流下 學下野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n次次跑步除左頭果1-2km 好易跑兩步覺得冇乜氣就轉左做行路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇咩跑法可以減少呢種休息時間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65df40a4ab2900932ee14ebaa819ff43e3c1693","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pish"},{"pid":"a955d7532f66b468f6a8ac9a9d18bac4ba4d432a","tid":298033,"uid":26669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"跑左幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  暫時最遠個次係荃灣西跑入屯門，我覺得岩岩開始個時唔洗對自己太高要求，跑一兩k抖500米，再跑一兩k抖500米，慢慢練就會有氣架啦"},{"pid":"0f2376b42895fc17b524b1744586a0259b6b21eb","tid":298033,"uid":39484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:44:46.000Z","msg":"每次跑耐少少 好快就跑到好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 連登冇人跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac502b9e11e15836879e037da4ff493356d72e5e","tid":298033,"uid":66104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"有啊 不過忙一星期跑一次炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956056d846f9cb18adce16a0ea28b49ac10fc1ae","tid":298033,"uid":86937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"跑幾多同幾耐係跟番你個人體能去制定<br />\n你冇理由冇做開運動然後訂一個目標係跑42K 馬拉松<br />\n所以一開始循序漸進先 跑一兩星期等身體適應左先<br />\n之後慢慢加長距離<br />\n<br />\nBTW 記得跑之前熱身 <br />\n同埋而家天氣熱 記得補充水份<br />\n當跑緊個時覺得唔舒服就停低休息下先<br />\n<br />\n利申跑左一年 個人經驗"},{"pid":"114a326cc3ce45335ca9b6244443414e625cd618","tid":298033,"uid":86937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"至於你覺得體能唔止咁差<br />\n應該可以跑多過1-2km<br />\n<br />\n可能係你跑步既tempo有問題<br />\n長跑唔係短跑<br />\n要注意自己呼吸既節奏同大唔大步<br />\n每個人有自己一套適合自己既跑法<br />\n呢樣要靠跑得多 然後自己搵出黎<br />\n文字好難教"},{"pid":"3c9798c5d4cd3fe83d64d0f80997efd7918c9821","tid":298033,"uid":105462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:57:15.000Z","msg":"自己定下跑既距離 or 時間之後行路休息<br />\n呢d要慢慢來   無得急"},{"pid":"b95449d38c297ab57c085a673f647865e6611b83","tid":298033,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"練時間 再練距離 再練番時間 再練番距離"},{"pid":"462e7c01cf7fcf770505ed959cb8dfb3ce04f576","tid":298033,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"每日廿分鐘"},{"pid":"2112f77e3fa0dea9e46647f5bc1bfe323a8a7451","tid":298033,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"跑開荃灣西到嘉頓來回，一齊跑吧"},{"pid":"192e0c717ba9e75d9775c178cf836d278830c10f","tid":298033,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎 慢慢跑多 木"},{"pid":"5cb78b07ab6e98cccb4911494d60dec49cd60036","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑開荃灣西到嘉頓來回，一齊跑吧</blockquote><br />\n荃灣西去深水埗？<br />\n我10km都要用90分鐘 應該跑一陣就唔見師兄車尾燈"},{"pid":"3ed0323c83bf3917d2f02dd16cb3ee01b887db6f","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>至於你覺得體能唔止咁差<br />\n應該可以跑多過1-2km<br />\n<br />\n可能係你跑步既tempo有問題<br />\n長跑唔係短跑<br />\n要注意自己呼吸既節奏同大唔大步<br />\n每個人有自己一套適合自己既跑法<br />\n呢樣要靠跑得多 然後自己搵出黎<br />\n文字好難教</blockquote><br />\n我都重係度試緊 體能仍然好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有節奏都冇用"},{"pid":"39ac24865967b6db21e1720371b0105526b331ca","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:20:51.000Z","msg":"仲有冇巴絲跑步？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0bfaca04a9d86613f574c692b973e8db2a96b8","tid":298033,"uid":96760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"揾個會跟操提升快好多"},{"pid":"8e3cddd26e2c4b0c011e95f78280823300965c04","tid":298033,"uid":77827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"跑左兩個月 食飯後跑半個鍾<br />\n除左落雨 唔舒服都keep住跑<br />\n近呢個禮拜唔知點解入面塞頭痛<br />\n尤其伸直隻腳<br />\n諗住停下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e967734ee9cade5fa59d8c50f964773071ac42c4","tid":298033,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跑開荃灣西到嘉頓來回，一齊跑吧</blockquote><br />\n荃灣西去深水埗？<br />\n我10km都要用90分鐘 應該跑一陣就唔見師兄車尾燈</blockquote><br />\n深井嘉頓啊，來回11k。<br />\n慢慢跑就會快"},{"pid":"a8f4996c8b650c35e8d4e91a9b286432a193b201","tid":298033,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4270d4dc1f4e27ef4146e5f79b4864a410a6aab","tid":298033,"uid":37600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑左兩個月 食飯後跑半個鍾<br />\n除左落雨 唔舒服都keep住跑<br />\n近呢個禮拜唔知點解入面塞頭痛<br />\n尤其伸直隻腳<br />\n諗住停下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就跑一個<span style=\"color: red;\">鐘</span><br />\n都係<span style=\"color: red;\">膝</span>頭痛<br />\nD人講到好大鑊<br />\n巴打你係唔係好重?"},{"pid":"ea74b247fb35f1e1b067bbeeb95f3e9e2c938c2f","tid":298033,"uid":119415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"荃灣跑步JJ留名<br />\n利申：慢步速"},{"pid":"bbbd62ee1de98c307d419df57f30b2972ad4a8f0","tid":298033,"uid":31866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"做足準備運動，跑慢D"},{"pid":"4b0a44076bbe9156acdc23df95c372475fe1515d","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做足準備運動，跑慢D</blockquote><br />\n我跑慢跑快都係差唔多距離收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7814247c5b87fae61cdcdfd523fd6f6d2de0f32c","tid":298033,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"跑馬路 上斜好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e325b6e6fe607e095e9dad55a0c2c39fe3e3c0","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑馬路 上斜好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上完大斜背跑多陣就冇氣<br />\n<br />\n諗緊有大斜轉做急行就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行路同跑差唔多速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec153325c43f2173be0439223323b7db3276c88e","tid":298033,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"各位 真係少啲跑馬路<br />\n吸塵唔多好"},{"pid":"2c7c12782a513d8cdfb7b224286cf3c00befc564","tid":298033,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"可以先將跑步節奏再放慢，等自己習慣跑耐少少<br />\n之後再慢慢升高番速度"},{"pid":"cd87f6cba2e61111845caf050fa99cab99d8b3fe","tid":298033,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"初跑 跑1-2k唔洗去到技術層次<br />\n最簡單 每次要求自己 堅持多小小<br />\n長跑係日積月累 打持久戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 跑左5年"},{"pid":"70b30e98be20f31ee71a436d88ae2e9afa4dcabe","tid":298033,"uid":77705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:09:21.000Z","msg":"之前晚晚都跑7k左右，跑左幾個月<br />\n之後膝頭痛停左幾個月冇跑<br />\n利申 沿荃灣西海旁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59d50f61728f4ad12b3a9c811214883be60ed32","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前晚晚都跑7k左右，跑左幾個月<br />\n之後膝頭痛停左幾個月冇跑<br />\n利申 沿荃灣西海旁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見好多人都傷膝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9cb56927fb6a7c3ac84a4f664ee8f1bbe9bd14","tid":298033,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"我反而係腳腕痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8121044d5dfee4f66753c646e5e4aef810de4181","tid":298033,"uid":123289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而係腳腕痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似話可以練大腿肌去保護膝頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁腳裸就小腿肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"714697e58786c709a19346f653783ea3f211eb2c","tid":298033,"uid":77827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跑左兩個月 食飯後跑半個鍾<br />\n除左落雨 唔舒服都keep住跑<br />\n近呢個禮拜唔知點解入面塞頭痛<br />\n尤其伸直隻腳<br />\n諗住停下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就跑一個<span style=\"color: red;\">鐘</span><br />\n都係<span style=\"color: red;\">膝</span>頭痛<br />\nD人講到好大鑊<br />\n巴打你係唔係好重?</blockquote><br />\n係啊 5十幾kg 絲打"},{"pid":"73e0a73941bd5e58d1f630e2cb0545cf29825d29","tid":298033,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s